# 📘 Unified Reporting Utility – Technical Design Document

---

# 1. 📌 Overview

## 1.1 Purpose

Design a **centralized .NET-based utility** to:

* Execute existing PowerShell scripts (unchanged logic)
* Handle email delivery centrally
* Reduce scheduler duplication
* Improve maintainability and scalability

---

## 1.2 Scope

✔ Reuse existing scripts (HealthCheck, License, Performance)
✔ Remove email logic from scripts
✔ Support multiple execution modes
✔ Provide flexible configuration

---

